@startsalt architecture
{#
<b>Layer 1: Data Sources
. AQICN API | Google Air Quality API | IQAir API
--
<b>Layer 2: Ingestion & Processing  
. Ingestion Job (10 min cycle - 216 readings/hour)
. Normalizer | Validator
--
<b>Layer 3: Data Persistence
. PostgreSQL (8 entities, 3NF) | MongoDB (Preferences)
--
<b>Layer 4: Application & API
. FastAPI REST | Redis Cache | PgBouncer | Recommendation Engine
--
<b>Layer 5: Presentation
. React/Vue Dashboard | Real-time Charts | Heatmaps
}
@endsalt
